title: Complete Goodyear Christmas Albums Vol 5
description:
From 1965, courtesy of the Christmas Shario blog, here is Volume 5 in the series of Christmas albums released each year by Goodyear as a promotional item.  For many of us boomers, these are the Christmas soundtracks of our memories.  Volume 5 is my personal favorite. 

01 Andy Williams - O Holy Night
02 Andre Kostelanetz - It Came Upon A Midnight Clear
03 Anna Maria Alberghetti - Caroling, Caroling
04 Maurice Chevalier - Jolly Old Saint Nicholas
05 Eugene Ormandy - Little Drummer Boy
06 Anna Maria Alberghetti - Star Carol
07 Eugene Ormandy & Philadelphia Orchestra - We Three Kings
08 Andre Kostelanetz - Hark, the Herald Angels Sing
09 Maurice Chevalier - Silent Night
10 Richard Tucker - The Lord&#039;s Prayer
11 Steve Lawrence & Eydie Gorme - Sleigh Ride
12 Dinah Shore - The Twelve Days of Christmas
13 Richard Tucker - O Little Town of Bethlehem
14 Diahann Carroll - Lo, How A Rose
15 Diahann Carroll - Some Children See Him
16 Danny Kaye - O Come All Ye Faithful/The First Noel
17 Doris Day - Silver Bells
18 Sammy Davis Jr. - Jingle Bells/It&#039;s Christmas Time
